content: Other net sales, which principally include pop-up shop and shop-in shop net sales, increased $11.2 million or 164.9% to $18 million in the fourth quarter of fiscal 2022 as compared to $6.8 million in the prior year period given the higher productivity of our Costco.com pop-ups in addition to the one additional pop-up shop during the fourth quarter of fiscal 2022 and the increase in Best Buy shop-in shops just discussed.
